# Example environment file for Claude Code Development Environment
# Copy this file to .env.host and customize with your details

# Git Configuration (REQUIRED)
# Replace with your actual name and email for git commits
GIT_USER_NAME="Your Name"
GIT_USER_EMAIL="your.email@example.com"

# Optional: Additional environment variables
# CLAUDE_API_KEY=your-claude-api-key-here
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key-here

# To use this file:
# 1. Copy: cp .env.host.example .env.host
# 2. Edit .env.host with your actual details
# 3. The Makefile will automatically load it when starting containers